{"article_id":"ynTlAkFPnEihW3Lp","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump knew about the six-figure payment","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that was made to porn actress Stormy Daniels `` several months ''","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"before he denied any knowledge of it","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"when speaking to reporters onboard Air Force One last month ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"The New York Times reported Friday .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Questions about the payment resurfaced earlier this week","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"after Trump 's attorney , former New York City mayor Rudy Giuliani , said","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that the president repaid Michael Cohen for money","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"given to Daniels","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"to keep quiet about an alleged affair","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"she had with Trump .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"Citing people familiar with the matter ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"the Times reported","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"that Trump knew","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Cohen , his personal attorney , had succeeded","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"in silencing Daniels ' allegations at the time","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"he denied knowing about the hush money in April .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"The Times report did not mention exactly","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"when Trump learned about the payment .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"Changing his story Thursday ,","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"Trump acknowledged","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"a $ 130,000 payment to Daniels ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"whose real name is Stephanie Clifford ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"but said","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"a non-disclosure agreement was `` used","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"to stop the false and extortionist accusations","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"made by her about an affair . ''","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"On Friday , Giuliani issued a statement","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"he made mistakes","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"regarding a timeline on the Daniels payment","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"which came","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"hours after Trump rebuked him ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"telling reporters","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"the ex-New York City mayor needs to get his stories straight .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"The Times also mentioned","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"that Trump Organization chief financial officer Allen Weisselberg has known since last year","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"that Cohen was being reimbursed in the form of $ 35,000 monthly payments .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"The money ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"according to the Times ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"came from the trust","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"that contains Trump 's personal fortune .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"The $ 130K question :","depth":4},{"id":43,"text":"What the White House has said about the Stormy Daniels payoff","depth":4},{"id":44,"text":"Fact Check :","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"Q & A on Stormy Daniels ' payment , Trump , Rudy Giuliani , Michael Cohen","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"Related :","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"President Trump , Rudy Giuliani try to again explain Stormy Daniels payment","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"Campaign finance groups said","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"the $ 130,000 payment ,","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"made less than two weeks before the 2016 election ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"amounted to an in-kind campaign contribution ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"and should have been reported as such .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"The organization Citizens for Responsibility and Ethics has filed a complaint with the Department of Justice and the Office of Government Ethics","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"asking them to investigate","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"whether Giuliani ' s disclosures show","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"that Trump violated federal ethics laws or laws against making false statements","de